title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. Currently, the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 2. The query result should be stored in the output parameter as an object.
